Portions of this product are derived from the "vscode-magma" Visual Studio Code
extension by Erkan Tairi:

    https://github.com/etairi/vscode-magma

Specifically, the following components are derived from that project and remain
under the original MIT License (see LICENSE-MIT):

  * The Magma keyword, operator, type-category and built-in function lists
    used by the lexer (src/main/kotlin/.../MagmaKeywords.kt, MagmaTypes.kt,
    MagmaBuiltins.kt). These were extracted from the original TextMate grammar
    `syntaxes/magma.tmLanguage`.

  * The live template definitions in `src/main/resources/liveTemplates/Magma.xml`
    are direct ports of the snippets in the original `snippets/snippets.json`.

  * The plugin/file-type icon, derived from `images/magma-icon.png`.

